    <para id="import-auto-id1166547937786">Show that mean energy of electron in conduction band is (3/5)E<sub>F</sub> .</para>
    <list id="import-auto-id1166548117928" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic"><item>Q.3. Determine P(E<sub>F</sub> + kT) in Fermi-Dirac Statistics. Determine Temperature T at which P(E<sub>F</sub> + 0.5eV) = 1%.[Answers: 0.27, 1262Kel]</item>
